Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,UNRAVELING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[both] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[all] Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] This is him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Hmm.\NHe's nothing like I thought he'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yagami of the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mogi.\N-Ukita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, the five of us are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were Kira you would be dead,\NMr. Soichiro Yagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief of the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[all exclaiming]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira needs a face and a name\Nin order to commit murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure you've already figured\Nthat much out, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not give out\Nyour names so carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,let's value our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that he needed a face\Nto kill someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't remember any evidence\Nthat showed that he needed a name too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to verify\Nif this is related to criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,whose names were never released publicly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,or whose names were spelled incorrectly\Nin the media have not been targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We briefly went over it\Nat one of our meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] That's enough small talk for now.\NCome this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Please turn off\Nall your cellphones, handhelds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and any other communication devices
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave them on the table right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Do you think we're going to be\Nusing our cellphones during this meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to leak information?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Just do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] I realize he's been cautious\Nfrom the very beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still can't tell\Nif he trusts us or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] No, I just find them distracting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it when people's cellphones\Nare ringing while I'm trying to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me start by saying nobody takes notes\Non anything that's said in these meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That means, when we leave Headquarters,\Nany information we need
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is committed to memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, make yourselves comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[sips loudly]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[gulps loudly]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me, L?\N-[L] Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And from now on, I'll have to ask\Nthat you stop calling me "L."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Ryuzaki" now, just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay, Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,if we know that he needs\Na name and a face to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't we cut down on\Nthe number of victims
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,by keeping criminals' names from the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, we'll only be putting\Nthe general public at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-The general public?\N-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira is childish and he hates losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also childish and I hate to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind being\Na little more specific for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Early on in the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to provoke Kira\Nwith that broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Up until then, we thought\Nthat Kira would only go after criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But as we all witnessed,\Nhe didn't hesitate to kill my stand-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, as soon as I said we knew\Nhe was in the Kanto region,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in defiance, he made sure his next victims\Ncame from within Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,as if to say,\N"What are you gonna do about it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[slurps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's met each of my challenges head on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's never missed an opportunity\Nto return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what do you think would happen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,if we tried to use media restrictions\Nto hide criminals from someone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you choose to withhold the names\Nof your worst criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill petty criminals or the innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm holding the whole world hostage,\Nso who's it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the evil one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But all those who oppose me\Nby hiding criminals, you are truly evil."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[L sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly how Kira thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's look at another way\Nwe can use the media to draw him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Death of FBI agents infuriates the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Latest killings anger\Nthe international policing community.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nations agree to send 1,500 investigators\Nto Japan."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For Kira, this will be way beyond\Nwhat he faced with the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll see everyone as a potential threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychologically,\Nhe'll start to feel cornered,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and that will cause him\Nto take some kind of drastic action.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,T-- That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So he'll think there are 1,500,\Nwhen there really are only seven of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And since none\Nof these investigators exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira won't be able to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It just might work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, before we celebrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the rest of my thoughts\Non the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[all grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira works alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He had access\Nto all our classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What evidence do you have\Nthat he's working alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's listen to his entire theory\Nbefore asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We know he needs\Na name and a face to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And, to some extent,\Nhe can control a victim's' time of death
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and their actions before dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] We already know that much.\NPlease keep that in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and listen carefully\Nto what I have to say next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,On December 14,\Ntwelve FBI investigators entered Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ENTER JAPAN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we are on December 19…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Using prison inmates,\NKira conducts experiments,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,manipulating his victims' actions\Nbefore they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,12/19 TEST\N12/14 FBI (12) ENTER JAPAN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, during this window\Nof only five days,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira became aware of the FBI's presence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and obviously felt threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he didn't know\Nany of their names or faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,he was at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He needed to know how much control\Nhe had over his victims
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,before he could use it\Nagainst the twelve agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we all know, on December 27…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I got a hold of a file\Nwhich contained all the names and faces
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of the FBI investigators in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I succeeded\Nin killing each one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's practically impossible to guess\Nwhich agent gave the file to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to make sure\Nthat no one ever finds out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that I came into contact with Raye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,12/20 BUS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How come you're not using\Nthe Death Note today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You studying for those entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the least of my worries.\NPlus, it's a little late to start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,December 19 to December 27...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been most active during this period.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,During this period,\Nto the best of our knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,at least twenty-three individuals\Ndied of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But these victims were different\Nfrom Kira's previous targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all alleged criminals,\Nex-convicts,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,or suspects in ongoing investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, legally speaking, they were innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What this indicates is that Kira had\Nto manipulate these lesser criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to kill those FBI agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed that many people\Nso we'd be unable to tell the decoys
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from those who were actually used.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In truth, he probably only needed a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He waited eight days
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so the FBI could investigate\Nother suspects,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which meant there'd be no timeline\Nlinking him to their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect Kira had to be one of the people\Nbeing investigated by the FBI,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,between the 14th and the 19th of December.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I have no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These are files provided by the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And they contain additional information\Nyou might find useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For obvious reasons, you're not permitted\Nto take these out of this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-[Matsuda] Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There might only be five of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but with this much information,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we should be able to cover\Na lot of ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] We'll split into two teams.\NOne team traces the FBI agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the other looks at\Nthe heart attack victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There weren't that many people\Nwho had access
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to information from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And of those, the FBI only investigated\Na small group in the first five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, does anyone have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Actually, Ryuzaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have one question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And it pertains to what you said\Nto us earlier about how you hate to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the fact that you've shown us\Nyour face mean that you've lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By just being here,\Nare you admitting defeat to Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,By showing my face to you now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and by sacrificing the lives\Nof twelve FBI agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lost the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not going to lose the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time\NI've ever put my life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show Kira that we're all willing\Nto risk our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,if that's what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] And that justice will prevail,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then. Let's do this, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Well, I had my doubts\Nabout whether it was really him at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we go any further, I have to be\Nabsolutely sure that none of you are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll need to speak with each of you\Nindividually before you leave today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?\NHe still doesn't trust us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami]\NNo. I think it's a fair request.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to see it from his perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's been getting information\Nfrom our headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a good chance\Nthat he's one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief's right. Working this case\Nhas given us a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to see him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's risking his life to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Things are going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one clue, a single decisive factor,\Nis all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Just one oversight...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A single piece of evidence\Nis all it would take.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It could cost me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just one thing…\N-Just one thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[cars honking]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] You already finished studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. I haven't missed anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The biggest risk I've taken so far\Nwas that bus-jacking incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But they'll never be able\Nto connect it with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately for me,\Nboth the police and L don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that Kira can kill people by means\Nother than a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if anyone were\Nto discover that fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Does it have to be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father's been pulling overnighters\Nwith no change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to bring this to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Mom, I totally promised my friends\Nthat I'd go out with them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I go? I could use a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you one next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I guess this'll give you a chance\Nto spy on the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go further\Nthan the reception desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[suspenseful music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Oh, you're bringing a page?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Planning to kill someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but lately, I've been bringing\Na page with me every time I go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] That day…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye said that he was planning\Nto go to Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That same day, four people died\Nof heart attacks in the Shinjuku area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And... there was the bus-jacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,BUS-JACKER DIES\NAFTER BEING HIT BY CAR
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it was a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,NATIONAL POLICE AGENCY\NAND PUBLIC SAFETY COMMISSION
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira can kill in other ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile customer\Nyou are trying to reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unusual for Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I wonder if he's in a meeting\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to speak directly with someone\Nfrom the special investigation Task Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, ma'am, but I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As I've told you already, there is no one\Nat Task Force headquarters right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one at Headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's cell is turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] Can't you contact them somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have information\Nrelating to the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kira investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'll call Headquarters\None more time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Detective Soichiro Yagami's son,\NLight Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought my father a change of clothes\Nbut it doesn't look like he's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I leave them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Hey,\NI haven't seen you in a while, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped solve the insurance fraud\Nmurder investigation sometime last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But, hey, no one remembers a receptionist,\Ndo they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. I'm terrible with faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to sign my name\Non this form, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Light, does this mean
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to be helping us\Nwith the Kira investigation too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, if all goes well,\Nmaybe I'll find Kira before L does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him before L does?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought,\Nthere's no one at Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to trust me\Non this, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to give them your message\Nas soon as I see them, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] That's not good enough.\NI have to tell them in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is actually in charge\Nof the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, I could pass your message\Non to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,His cellphone is off at the moment,\Nbut I should be able to contact him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A number of FBI agents were just killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of detectives have quit the case\Nbecause they're afraid of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's pretty busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Light, it's probably better\Nif you don't discuss this with...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,True, but it's practically\Ncommon knowledge at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I feel like I can trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can almost see it in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a wise and careful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard about what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you must have figured out\Nthat the police had a leak of some kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you wanted\Nto tell them in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure my father will be calling me back\Nonce he checks his messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When he does, I'll give you the phone\Nand let you talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure that's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand why I can't just give you\Nmy father's cellphone number,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have no problem letting you\Nuse my phone to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to trust my father and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which I hope won't be\Ntoo difficult for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Why is he so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She walked right into that one,\Ndidn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta say,\Nyou must be pretty brave
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to be getting involved\Nin the Kira case like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi sighs] Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] So, according to you,\Nis Kira some...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[clears throat]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we've been talking, and I just\Nrealized I don't even know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Light's written\Nwith the character for "moon"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and Yagami with the characters\Nfor "night" and "god."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda weird, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Shoko Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written with the characters\Nfor "shining."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ko" as in "child" and "ki" as in "tree."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Maki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ms. Maki,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about Kira's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I believe they enable him\Nto somehow control his victims
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,before they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's odd that you say that because\Nthat's exactly what I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's able to control their actions\Nbefore he kills them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If my analysis so far is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira can kill in a number of ways,\Nnot just with a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] She knows? Who is this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone else knows this yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the police\Nare willing to consider it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it would help them catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that possibility\Nnever even crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what you're saying is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,any time Kira wants one of his murders\Nto go undetected,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he wouldn't use a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost positive that someone I know\Nmay have met Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Met Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but if a person came in\Nsaying they'd met Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the police would be more\Nthan a little skeptical, to say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need to explain it in person\Nto someone from Task Force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'm afraid\Nthey'd just write me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't it be better\Nif your friend spoke to them instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably would,\Nbut he's no longer alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He was one of the twelve FBI agents\Nwho came to Japan to investigate Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,An FBI agent who met Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Naomi] You see, he was also my fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,While he was working, he got caught up\Nin a bus-jacking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have reason to believe\Nthat he met Kira on that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye Penber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I'm sorry to hear\Nthat he passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So... what makes you think\Nhe met Kira on that bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because eight days\Nafter that bus was hijacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,he died, along with the other\NFBI investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The same man had attempted to rob a bank\Ntwo days before he hijacked that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And he dies in an accident?\NJust like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, really, what are the odds?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to believe\Nthat Kira set up that bus-jacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was planned to bring him\Ninto contact with my fiancé,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to obtain information regarding\Nthe identities of the other FBI agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so he could get rid of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what stands out to me\Nis that the hijacker died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it suggests that heart attacks\Naren't the only way Kira can kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Okay, so the bus-jacker\Ndidn't die of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And based on that, you're saying\NKira has other ways of killing people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take this the wrong way, but I think\Nthat's a bit of a leap of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way of looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kira was controlling the hijacker,\Nchances are he killed him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I still don't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering about that bus-jacking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since my fiancé\Nfirst told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After he calmed down,\NI asked him for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't mention any names\Nor anything like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-but he told me one thing.\N-[Light] What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That he'd been put in a situation where\Nhe had to show his FBI ID to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation was undertaken secretly\Nwithout the NPA's knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't allowed to show his ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, whoever saw his ID that day
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,was responsible for the deaths\Nof all of the agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Unbelievable. She figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the oversight\NLight was worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who knows any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want nothing more\Nthan to avenge your fiancé
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,by bringing Kira to justice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're convinced that Kira\Ncan kill without using a heart attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] There's no doubt in my mind\Nyour deductive skills are excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't deny that you have\Na personal interest in the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, your theory is worth looking into.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your testimony could be central\Nto the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It could.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If what you're telling me is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then it will only be a matter of time\Nbefore the police catch up with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The person your fiancé showed his ID to\Non the bus that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it had to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If she'd spoken to the police\Nbefore I met her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems there's a god\Non my side after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just a god of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]